{"tid":1533080,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[戰略] 輸出革命正式啟動","createTime":"2019-09-02T16:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T02:33:03.000Z","uid":218652,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8e4307448b1c08aaa2c94c460d6678b755849241","tid":1533080,"uid":218652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:09:35.000Z","msg":"我知連登好多大學生，所以<br />\n<br />\n<strong>[size=4<span style=\"color: red;\">]我宣佈內地生狂熱關懷戰線正式啟動!</span>[/size=4]</strong><br />\n<br />\n大量內地生來港讀書，好多已經到步! 我地作為同學務必要噓寒問暖，同佢地做好朋友，將社會最真實的一面展示給他們。認真講，內地的每一篇新聞報導都要經過審查，資訊封鎖到恐怖的地步。有很多內地生根本無處接觸資訊，被強制變成無知可憐的人，完全接觸不到真相，活在中共建構的世界裡。<br />\n<br />\n其實佢地好多都係理性，肯聽肯討論 ，以唔好為佢地戴上有色眼鏡，然後用友善的態度，潛移默化他們的思想帶回家。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 香港革命之父 梁天琦 都係大陸移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港民主嘅路上不能只有香港人。<br />\n<br />\n最後，<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c1d21864d6252b3b1273dfa56b434d8a12b2d6ff","tid":1533080,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:10:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我推到同溫層既大家知道<br />\n你地負責幫手去fb啊等等宣傳得唔得<br />\n唔好再理膠post喇 關注返行動post<br />\n再好好運用6月至今每個核彈去twitter做文宣喇<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgUXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=d559a486\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，<br />\n請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n-大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n-高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n-高舉大量國旗<br />\n-唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼 補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n-領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"0af96ee320d3850ab2f0cb13511371be64700cfc","tid":1533080,"uid":218652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:11:00.000Z","msg":"自推十連 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"073f634309bd9fa918eb8144378b44d698ae461d","tid":1533080,"uid":218652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:11:18.000Z","msg":"自推十連 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2/10"},{"pid":"9bee85b0670e7f49e61755d45a98e12c77daadb2","tid":1533080,"uid":218652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:11:31.000Z","msg":"自推十連 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3/10"},{"pid":"d0b17d17a08c81e2bc87dc5166c3463171aa2788","tid":1533080,"uid":218652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:11:41.000Z","msg":"自推十連 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4/10"},{"pid":"9b6a6a09b3e03b121083a11244b50a629b526ce1","tid":1533080,"uid":218652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:11:56.000Z","msg":"自推十連 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5/10"},{"pid":"2f588789817414087e17f41632b57b463c17c18a","tid":1533080,"uid":218652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:12:21.000Z","msg":"自推十連 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6/10"},{"pi